name: Uprising: The Flood
description:
First installment of the "Uprising" Series.
The mountains gain emotional expression, and their tears form a cleansing ocean that washes away all harm to the Mother Heart.
Be with Mama Earth... let her know you are grateful for her presence. Be mindful always, and breathe with the trees and the sky. Place your bare feet on the ground and dance like a wild animal, because we have all been holding this emotional baggage under weights for too long. Just let it go.
